    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>English and American 18th-century tables made to provide the facilities of the modern bathroom, with provisions for a basin, bottles, bidet, and other toilet equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
